# Branch and PR workflow

- For implementation work, never stay on `main`; create/use a feature branch first.
- Before committing, verify current branch is not `main` or `master`.
- After completing a slice, push branch and open/update a PR.
- If a PR supersedes another open PR, cross-link both and close the superseded one.
- Keep `PLAN.md` synchronized in the same pass whenever behavior/backlog changes materially.
